@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Ask a question - normal case
POST {{baseUrl}}/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Which property has the highest cap rate?"
}

### Ask a question - empty question (expect 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": ""
}

### Ask a question - missing field (expect 422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{}
